Articles.Content:
Hello!

I got blender about two weeks ago with the intent of making a KSP mod. So far I have made two parts, a NERVA engine, and Soyuz type capsule. Neither have been textured and they are very noobish looking, but here you go.

<iframe width="640" height="480" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>

[Nuke Engine](https://sketchfab.com/models/71d0e594af6540d69b6f700aa2c8cfb2) by [smallfatfetus](https://sketchfab.com/SmallFatFetus) on [Sketchfab](https://sketchfab.com)

<iframe width="640" height="480" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>

[Soyuz-ish](https://sketchfab.com/models/bd66a09927d546bd9f883b1b485612df) by [smallfatfetus](https://sketchfab.com/SmallFatFetus) on [Sketchfab](https://sketchfab.com)

Enjoy! If you want the .blend files and/or are willing to texture, pm me.

SmalllFatFetus
Welcome to the club! Good start on the models too.
